# Keep the build context to the source tree: no VCS history, no host build
# output (the image does its own release build), no Node artifacts.
# tools/jhm + make_dep_file are host-built (gitignored) binaries; if they
# leak into the context, `make bootstrap` skips bootstrap.sh and the .jhm
# tree-root marker it creates, and jhm dies at "Unable to find .jhm".
.git
.claude
tools/jhm
tools/make_dep_file
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/__pycache__
**/package-lock.json
*.log
